cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.AR, cs.SY. 

This paper is about predicting the energy consumption of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and optimizing their energy efficiency. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also deals with hardware and system-level optimization, which makes cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) possible sub-categories as well.
